definition: (of sth) to move/to set in movement/to displace/to touch/to make use of/to stir (emotions)/to alter/abbr. for 動詞|动词[dong4 ci2], verb

sentences.english: There is also a Children's Corner in our zoo.

sentences.chinese: 目的成功制作激素性骨坏死的动物模型。

sentences.english: The sources of Chinese medicine are mainly floras, also includes animals and mineral.

sentences.english: The temperature of cold-blooded animals change with the temperature of the surroundings .
